#1801
A room in mud school.~
Inside the watch house, the air is filled with the sweet smell of a fresh
cauldron of hot cocoa and armor polish.  Directly in front of the door is
a large counter with a registry book facing whomever would be sitting behind
it, were the post not currently vacant.
 
To the south is the main bullpen where the officers of the Watch go about
their daily business.  On the wall beside the counter is another note.
