#1802
The Bullpen~
Just past the main counter is a large room with rows of desks. Each desk
has the normal paraphenalia expected of someone who may, or may not, have
at least attended basic schooling.  Inkwells and quills can be seen on the
desks, and on a few of them random articles from the Ankh-Morpork Times can
be seen, some with words underlined or circled, and others with quite childish
and crude defacing of the pictures that accompany articles about those in the
higher social circles of Ankh-Morpork.
 
Leading up to the offices above is a stairway, and another leading down to the cells.
To the west, the smell of cocoa becomes much stronger as it wafts from the kitchen,
and to the east is a small supply closet with the door left wide open. To the south
is the door to the rear yard of the Watch House.  There is another note beside the door.
~
