#1803
Supply Closet~
Inside this closet, things are in a sad state of affairs...
 
Boxes of shoe polish containers, empty inkwells, shackles, unengraved badges,
and various other refuse have been tossed and stuffed on various shelves with
absolutely not regard to organization or even the smallest degree of
common sense.  There is something cold and unnatural about this room, as if in
the chaos of it's non-uniformity, it has created a connection with some sort
of otherworldly place.

 ...Or, it could just be nothing.
